data.description: LOCATION! LOCATION! NO FLOODING at any time! Just minutes from IAH, shopping, schools & hospitals. This four-bedroom, 3 1/2 bath home features granite countertops, Vaulted entry, freshly interior painted, new seamless shower doors installed in master bath,  Newer real hardwood floor in the office, and dining areas, Newer Carpet in 2018. Plantation Shutters throughout and vaulted ceilings in the formal living space. Enjoy quiet nights on the slate-tile back patio, very private with no back neighbors and orange tree. You will enjoy the open floor plan with Game Room up, MASTER DOWN, three spacious bedrooms up, CHEF'S kitchen with island and breakfast bar.  This home features an extra-long driveway with attached porte-cochere and detached double garage.   Community swimming pool, splash pad, parks and is in a golf course community.
